description.en:
Stablz is a stablecoin yield aggregator that converts yield to the same type as deposits. Deposit USDT, earn your yield in USDT in a truly set and forget manner. 

Token utility includes governance, usdt staking rewards, buybacks, and powering the referral program. 

In the future we will add non-stable asset pools such as ETH, or high APY farms and secure the yield in stablecoins.
